{"tid":2138091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳 Citysuper 染紅　彭博：華潤牽頭財團將購入多數股權","createTime":"2020-08-03T11:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T14:11:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"197441d4b0c5c2a49c2817668906710e60f40f3b","tid":2138091,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:12:12.000Z","msg":"再有本地零售品牌「染紅」，彭博通訊社報道，華潤集團牽頭的財團計劃收購本地高檔超市 Citysuper 多數股權，交易作價相當於業務估值約 3 億美元（約 23.4 億港元），報道引述消息指雙方最快本周簽訂交易協議。<br />\n<br />\nCitysuper 目前約 61% 股權由三黃集團持有，其餘約 39% 股份則由九倉系大股東吳光正持有。報道指出，吳光正家族亦有意出售所持的部分股權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/傳-citysuper-染紅-彭博-華潤牽頭財團將購入多數股權/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E5%82%B3-citysuper-%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85-%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E8%8F%AF%E6%BD%A4%E7%89%BD%E9%A0%AD%E8%B2%A1%E5%9C%98%E5%B0%87%E8%B3%BC%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B8%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=44c68ac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E5%82%B3-citysuper-%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85-%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E8%8F%AF%E6%BD%A4%E7%89%BD%E9%A0%AD%E8%B2%A1%E5%9C%98%E5%B0%87%E8%B3%BC%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B8%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A%2F&h=d5d08e93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/傳-citysuper-染紅-彭博-華潤牽頭財團將購入多數股權/</a>"},{"pid":"fe72d0eb0351ec082097e1fba19459762481bac9","tid":2138091,"uid":47356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"藍city"},{"pid":"9043e3b922327472afef1bf3dd7792d5e84325ec","tid":2138091,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"藍轉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95412f563702d3f1e4f438e174dd0cb30c1456de","tid":2138091,"uid":123264,"lik